data.description: Located across from the park and community pool this well maintained Townhome has black appliances and open kitchen/family room.  All three bedrooms are on the second floor with the master suite overlooking your fenced courtyard that is perfect for outdoor barbecues and soaking up the Florida sun.  Two-car garage with additional parking available in the driveway and in the street in front of the townhome.  Walk out your front door for an easy stroll to the community pool and park or take a walk around the neighborhood on paved sidewalks.  Conveniently located near Disney, Winter Garden Village shopping, downtown Windermere and highly regarded Orange County schools.
